OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775628243
OL,3,CPilot scheme launches to change
OL,4,Cbehaviour of high-risk domestic abusers
OL,6,FA pilot scheme is being launched in
OL,7,FSouthampton aimed at changing the
OL,8,Fbehaviour of those who carry out
OL,9,Fdomestic abuse.
OL,11,FThe Drive Project is a first for
OL,12,FHampshire and will bring together
OL,13,Fagencies such as the police,
OL,14,Fprobation, child and adult services
OL,15,Fand housing.
OL,17,FIt will work to change the behaviour
OL,18,Fof high-risk, high-harm domestic abuse
OL,19,Fperpetrators by intervening early to
OL,20,Fhelp prevent further harm.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
