PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775628243
OL,3,CPilot scheme launches to change
OL,4,Cbehaviour of high-risk domestic abusers
OL,6,FThe pilot will look to address the
OL,7,Froot causes of abuse through intensive
OL,8,Fone-to-one case management, including
OL,9,Fwork to address drug and alcohol
OL,10,Fdependency.
OL,12,FFigures suggest that two women a week
OL,13,Fdie in the UK as a result of domestic
OL,14,Fabuse while 100,000 people a year are
OL,15,Fat high risk of being murdered or
OL,16,Fseriously harmed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
