FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775628243
OL,3,CPilot scheme launches to change
OL,4,Cbehaviour of high-risk domestic abusers
OL,6,FThe project is being paid for with
OL,7,Fmore than half a million pounds of
OL,8,FHome Office funding and delivered
OL,9,Fthrough Police and Crime Commissioner
OL,10,FDonna Jones.
OL,12,FPCC Donna Jones said: "I am committed
OL,13,Fto the pursuit of high-risk
OL,14,Fperpetrators who pose a risk to women
OL,15,Fand girls, either at home or on the
OL,16,Fstreets.
OL,18,F"Too often they're not held to
OL,19,Faccount, and their abusive behaviour
OL,20,Fcontinues.
OL,26,@tD@WOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
