PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775628243
OL,3,CPilot scheme launches to change
OL,4,Cbehaviour of high-risk domestic abusers
OL,6,FUp to 120 perpetrators a year will be
OL,7,Fseen through the pilot, delivered by
OL,8,FHampshire-based domestic abuse
OL,9,Fcharity, Hampton Trust.
OL,11,FChief Executive of Hampton Trust,
OL,12,FChantal Hughes, said: "The Drive
OL,13,FProject targets those who pose the
OL,14,Fhighest risk to victims. This is where
OL,15,Fintensive, coordinated action is
OL,16,Fneeded most, and where the
OL,17,Fconsequences of doing nothing are most
OL,18,Fsevere.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
