PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775628243
OL,3,CPilot scheme launches to change
OL,4,Cbehaviour of high-risk domestic abusers
OL,6,F"We know that many people causing harm
OL,7,Fare also dealing with their own
OL,8,Fchallenges, such as mental health and
OL,9,Fdrug and alcohol use, and that these
OL,10,Fneed to be addressed if we are to
OL,11,Fachieve lasting change."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
